# Self Introduction Video

## About Me

Hello! My name is **Devi Sai Prasanna**, and I am a third-year Computer Science Engineering student with a strong interest in software development, artificial intelligence, and problem-solving.

I believe the best way to learn is by building, experimenting, and continuously improving through experience. I enjoy taking ideas from concept to implementation and using technology to create solutions that address real-world challenges.

Over time, I have worked on various projects that have helped me strengthen my technical skills, teamwork, and ability to learn new technologies quickly. My interests span across software engineering, AI-powered applications, and full-stack development.

